<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">In this area, you create and edit new contents for the header. At the moment, the header you create is globally active for all pages that have been created with the ShopBuilder. The same thing applies to the <strong>footer elements</strong>. <em>*Note*</em>: This section is collapsed by default.</p></td>
