<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Most widgets have additional settings that can be opened by clicking the <strong>gear wheel</strong> button. The widget settings are then displayed on the right side of the editor view. Widget settings are carried out for each individual widget; changes to one widget do not affect another widget of the same type.</p></td>
